summary: This module implements an optional hook import mechanism for Apache HTTP Server. It registers a test hook function that logs when the optional hook is called with a string parameter.

logs.reason: This debug log is generated when the optional hook test function is called with a string parameter. It helps developers trace the execution of optional hooks in Apache modules.
logs.resolution: This is an informational debug-level log message used for development and debugging purposes. No resolution is required as it doesn't indicate an error condition.
